  "prompt": "Why is Pokemon go not working in India currently?",
  "response": "As of now, Pok\u00e9mon GO is technically available in India, but there have been some challenges and restrictions over the years. In the past, the game faced temporary bans and difficulties due to mapping restrictions in the country. Niantic, the game's developer, has been working to resolve these issues.\n\nIf you're experiencing specific problems with the game, it could be due to various reasons such as:\n\n1. Network connectivity issues\n2. App version not updated\n3. Server problems\n4. Device compatibility\n5. Location services not enabled\n\nFor the most accurate and current information about the game's status in India, I recommend checking:\n- Official Pok\u00e9mon GO website\n- Niantic's official communications\n- App Store/Play Store for any current issues\n- Pok\u00e9mon GO community forums",
